          <h1>Fuzzy Keyword Search on Spatial Data</h1> 
            <div> 
              <span class="name">
                <a href="http://www.ics.uci.edu/~salsubai/">Sattam Alsubaiee</a> 
              </span> 
              <span class="name"> 
